    public class SqlValidatorTest
extends SqlValidatorTestCase
    Concrete child class of SqlValidatorTestCase, containing lots of unit tests.

    If you want to run these same tests in a different environment, create a derived class whose SqlValidatorTestCase.getTester() returns a different implementation of SqlTester.
